body.description: Wrapper around Mistral large language models that use the Chat endpoint

inputParams.description: What sampling temperature to use, between 0.0 and 1.0. Higher values like 0.8 will make the output more random, while lower values like 0.2 will make it more focused and deterministic.
inputParams.label: Temperature
inputParams.name: temperature

inputParams.description: The maximum number of tokens to generate in the completion.
inputParams.label: Max Output Tokens
inputParams.name: maxOutputTokens

inputParams.description: Nucleus sampling, where the model considers the results of the tokens with top_p probability mass. So 0.1 means only the tokens comprising the top 10% probability mass are considered.
inputParams.label: Top Probability
inputParams.name: topP

inputParams.description: The seed to use for random sampling. If set, different calls will generate deterministic results.
inputParams.label: Random Seed
inputParams.name: randomSeed

inputParams.description: Whether to inject a safety prompt before all conversations.
inputParams.label: Safe Mode
inputParams.name: safeMode

inputParams.description: What sampling temperature to use, between 0.0 and 1.0. Higher values like 0.8 will make the output more random, while lower values like 0.2 will make it more focused and deterministic.
inputParams.label: Temperature
inputParams.name: temperature

inputParams.description: The maximum number of tokens to generate in the completion.
inputParams.label: Max Output Tokens
inputParams.name: maxOutputTokens

inputParams.description: Nucleus sampling, where the model considers the results of the tokens with top_p probability mass. So 0.1 means only the tokens comprising the top 10% probability mass are considered.
inputParams.label: Top Probability
inputParams.name: topP

inputParams.description: The seed to use for random sampling. If set, different calls will generate deterministic results.
inputParams.label: Random Seed
inputParams.name: randomSeed

inputParams.description: Whether to inject a safety prompt before all conversations.
inputParams.label: Safe Mode
inputParams.name: safeMode

body.description: Wrapper around Mistral large language models that use the Chat endpoint

inputParams.description: What sampling temperature to use, between 0.0 and 1.0. Higher values like 0.8 will make the output more random, while lower values like 0.2 will make it more focused and deterministic.
inputParams.label: Temperature
inputParams.name: temperature

inputParams.description: The maximum number of tokens to generate in the completion.
inputParams.label: Max Output Tokens
inputParams.name: maxOutputTokens

inputParams.description: Nucleus sampling, where the model considers the results of the tokens with top_p probability mass. So 0.1 means only the tokens comprising the top 10% probability mass are considered.
inputParams.label: Top Probability
inputParams.name: topP

inputParams.description: The seed to use for random sampling. If set, different calls will generate deterministic results.
inputParams.label: Random Seed
inputParams.name: randomSeed

inputParams.description: Whether to inject a safety prompt before all conversations.
inputParams.label: Safe Mode
inputParams.name: safeMode

body.name: chatMistralAI

body.description: Wrapper around Mistral large language models that use the Chat endpoint

inputParams.description: What sampling temperature to use, between 0.0 and 1.0. Higher values like 0.8 will make the output more random, while lower values like 0.2 will make it more focused and deterministic.
inputParams.label: Temperature
inputParams.name: temperature

inputParams.description: The maximum number of tokens to generate in the completion.
inputParams.label: Max Output Tokens
inputParams.name: maxOutputTokens

inputParams.description: Nucleus sampling, where the model considers the results of the tokens with top_p probability mass. So 0.1 means only the tokens comprising the top 10% probability mass are considered.
inputParams.label: Top Probability
inputParams.name: topP

inputParams.description: The seed to use for random sampling. If set, different calls will generate deterministic results.
inputParams.label: Random Seed
inputParams.name: randomSeed

inputParams.description: Whether to inject a safety prompt before all conversations.
inputParams.label: Safe Mode
inputParams.name: safeMode
